item.title: Please help!
item.dc:creator: @Continue Continue
item.description:
@Continue wrote:

SilentCJ:

HPBarFull isn’t declared in Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1.java.

I’m sure it’s that it cannot find the constructor Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(java.lang.String,int,int) in the Sprite class, or in your case, Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1. Either change the parameters or create a new constructor. A constructor is a method with the same name of the class file. Such as if I had this:

	public class Example { //class declared here
		public Example() { //constructor here
		}
	}
